@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Archived
Archived --> Completed : review
Completed --> Delivered : submit
Completed : entry / log card
Delivered --> Active : update
Active --> Closed : approve
Closed --> Approved : update
Active --> Archived : revert
Approved --> [*]
@enduml